<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/804324-thanks-for-the-review-the-value-and">Thanks for the review. The value and interest of this book has raised my interest. It appears most everyone recommends &#39;The Lions of Al-Rassan&#39;. What other books has this author written?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_804324'><a id="like_count_community_question_804324" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/804324?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F104101.The_Lions_of_Al_Rassan">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/804324-thanks-for-the-review-the-value-and">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/804324-thanks-for-the-review-the-value-and">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
