        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1539748899" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7540665013091396703">First GGK book, I eventually chose to read this before Tigana, i&apos;m happy I did. I&apos;m truly lost for words, this was simply a great experience. I can&apos;t find any fault with the world, characters or the story. <br/>Rodrigo and Ammar were my favorites among st so many awesome characters.<br/>I will definitely re-read this book later. I hope to read Tigana soon.</span>
  <span id="freeText7540665013091396703" style="display:none">First GGK book, I eventually chose to read this before Tigana, i'm happy I did. I'm truly lost for words, this was simply a great experience. I can't find any fault with the world, characters or the story. <br />Rodrigo and Ammar were my favorites among st so many awesome characters.<br />I will definitely re-read this book later. I hope to read Tigana soon.</span>
