<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17535876810636946639">Guy Gavriel Kay is a Canadian author of fantasy fiction. Many of his novels are set in fictional realms that resemble real places during real historical periods, such as Constantinople during the reign of Justinian I or Spain during the time of El Cid. Those works are published and marketed as historical fantasy, though the author himself has expressed a preference to shy away from genre categoriz</span>
  <span id="freeText17535876810636946639" style="display:none">Guy Gavriel Kay is a Canadian author of fantasy fiction. Many of his novels are set in fictional realms that resemble real places during real historical periods, such as Constantinople during the reign of Justinian I or Spain during the time of El Cid. Those works are published and marketed as historical fantasy, though the author himself has expressed a preference to shy away from genre categorization when possible.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17535876810636946639" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
